Class PollResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.ReceiveSE
      • com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.Response
        • com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.PollResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PollResponse
extends Response
    Use this to access poll response information, as provided in an EPP poll response compliant with RFC5730. Such a service element is sent by an EPP server in response to a poll service element. If in response to a poll request, the getResData, getContactTransferResponse or getDomainTransferResponse methods may return object-specific information, which is in addition to any message queue data potentially available via the getMessage and related methods in the Response class.
    See Also:
    PollCommand, PollRequestCommand, PollAckCommand, Serialized Form
